Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beductio flows with the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark stains are rinsed clean and exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Danger-is√©stilll in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to be sharp to capture the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(57a 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(DH * X
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am 7 WW 4c
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we 9%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to meet with Heij and Kazuha, but they did not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided to go look for them .
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We called on Mr. Kusukawa, the detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and foundiout they went to a certain tou residence on Kashikobashi street, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're hungry, aren't you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But could you wait a little while, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mom is busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I finish my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll feed you right away, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must let them know where they stand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and teach them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji Hattori No Way Out\NPart 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuts! Wherelar those Osaka kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wandering around?\NI'm completely tired out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, dad. Let's have lunch and then start searchinglfondhe Item's again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could have passed them on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to have lunch at this old restaurant at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use complaining now, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides I Kd of like this house. It's old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old fashioned, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't see a horoscope dispenser so often any more thesexdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make another phone call, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may have gone to my detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, dad. I've tried calling from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the phone won't connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?\NGive me the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!\NWhere on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SOD. SONY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with Mr. Kusukawa.\NIn a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been talking about detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,business and forgot to get in touch with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is Kazuha there with you-too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, pops.\NI'd like to ask you a favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we have a cipher and we want you to solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cipher?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusukawa made the cipher and I promised
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried everything but I couldn't solve it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I thought of getting your help while Mr. Kusukawa is out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Mr. Kusukawa is not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of his Mahjong pals called him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They need one more player.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went outside to tell them he can't make it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I will mail the cipher on the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You send me the solution by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me know the seven numerals hidden in that cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven numerals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't-solve it, I can't come to you, so hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smart kid you are to let Kogoro\NMouri think it over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we need to mail the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He soiled the paper with his blood\NSO we can't read the lower half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?\NDidn't you make a copy of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. After we got that cipher, were busy interrogating Kusukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have memorized all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,49 numerals and the order of the alphabets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, really? Then, tell me all 49\NIetters without looking at the paper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if you give me even one wrong number,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you will get stained with the blood of that girlfriend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's thisyy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't make any sense out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numerals and, four alphabets\NQ A. K, J, these could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what they are supposed to mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:06:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Heiji said he won't budge an inch until he solves this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan? Did you find out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see? These letters, A. J, Q, and K remind me of the letters on playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I've changed them into numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the numbers turned out to be 64 in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bu WM noticed that there is onedllone number
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's the nine in the center.\NThere's' only one nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take that nine, and the remaining 63 numerals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will make 7 grips of 9 numerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there are seven numerals in this cipher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,each of the seven groups should be a certain number
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't solve it like math.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've just made more numbers that you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are, the diced steaks, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just the thing\NI've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi. This 1s the Kidrs Lunch Plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, pops. Can it be\NMr. KusuRawa who coded this cipher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why the center is a nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here is your omelet- Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! It"looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rather simple, once you figure out how to Give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, this looks strange. The first four are numerals but the lastethree are not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait\NI saw these somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now the time is up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to go, otherwise we won't make it in time to use the safe-deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to blame someone, blame it on that incompetent detective of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! I may be able to solve it overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can go to the bank tomorrow before the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ietter is delivered to the detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are not worried about it.\NBecause the letter will not be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hey, you are not going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll ambush the deliveryman in front of the office and rob him of the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will keep paying the fee for using
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the safe into the bank account of Kusukawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the tape will not come out into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will take time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to solve the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike you guys. I have unlimited time on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now. If you have anything\Nleft to say, I'll listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To listen to a person with genuine concern is a duty for a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn! Kudo, you dumbbell.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to have any concern for this world, well then, as you wish
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do, I do. I have a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have so many things to say that I was at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More than anything else, I want to say a word to the girl behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow. What do you want to say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know she will be dead soon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very important things to say that I wanted to tell her for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, would you mind putting your gun on the floor while I talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well. After all, you are high school kids. Excuse me for being dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This will do, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can start telling her, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am choosing the best words for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she will be impressed and can go to heaven with those words of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be fascinating and, wonderful words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pity, Heiji. It was such a good strategy for taking the gun from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trategy, was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we are lucky to find the guy who made the cipher to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me the answer to the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to see the head of your kid friend here blown apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell her, Mr. Kusukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do, it'll only buy you a little more time to go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's make them regret what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You talk too much, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up! Give me the answer before I count up to five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I won't hesitate to fire at the first person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really mean it, Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to tell you before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell you many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were back to back and I felt you trembling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. A mail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They couldn't possibly have solved the cipher so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like an answer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't they just send back what we sent them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Some of the numerals and alphabets are in different order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!\NHey, give me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. No. Uh. Could I take a look at it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks exactly like the cipher I gave you to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks exactly like the cipher I gave you to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks very much like it, yeah\NBut, this is an answer to the mail we sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This says they found the seven numerals hidden in the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are not making it up, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, you don't know what a sorry pickle you're in, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know what pickle you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri knows the answer to the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, he knows that Mr.\NKusukawa made the cipher, and also that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are with Mr. Kusukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we three disappeared at one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that will make the detective think hard and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he will find out the meaning of the seven numerals hidden in the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that the 7 digit number is an ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will take less than a week to find them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sent your cipher to Kogoro Mouri knowing what he will do all the while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be in big trouble, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can kill them and run, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You talk too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have only two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You Kill us and let Mouri get the tape and listen to it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or let me go get the tape, and exchange us for the tape
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mr. Kusukawa can go instead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he can't possibly play the role with that swollen face of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm telling you I will go instead of him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, listen, if as Mr. Kusukawa told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you stop doing bad things and promise not to kill us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't turn you in to the police, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to get the tape and rush it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of you can come with me to watch over me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and keep me from doing anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have much time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't get going now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we won't make it in time for using the safe-deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. OK. I will accept your terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the answer to the cipher proves wrong, you know what will become of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Heiji can go with me, and the young lady
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,can stay here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If, if we make it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we make it through, will you tell me what you were going to tell me me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll keep on telling you until you get tired of hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as we get a phone call from her saying that she's got the tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll set fire .
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid will be surprised to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you are not in front of the house waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are inside the house and that it's on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now Heiji, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quick about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enter the seven numbers hidden in the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't ou want to know how to solve the cipher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since that cipher was made by\NMr. Kusukawa, the gambling man,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can easily see that those A, J,\NQ, and K are of playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-- OD)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Change them into numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we have 64 numerals in all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, something bothers me and it's a 9 in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are lots of 1 to-6 numbers but only one 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when it hit me that if I take out the 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can divide the remaining 63 numerals by 9 and get 7 groups of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These 7 groups of numbers can stand for a 7-digit number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all numbers are in 1 to 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a gambling man, 1 to 6 means only one thing, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A die Of the dice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means put the 9 numerals of 7 groups into
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means put the 9 numeraso Qroups no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The form of dice of 3 by 3 squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4 A a4 ta O su a )\NJ lll$fill the form of dice of 3 by 3 squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what and where are the 7 numerals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's change the numbers into the dots of dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And imagine we are looking at the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,29464303
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,striking, now you can read the seven numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,striking, now you can read the seven numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the number comes up to 3156204
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading the dice, it's 3156204
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably, the cipher was made into squares with the center to be 9
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because of the image of dice and dots on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There! Look! It's opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is it! The tape you wanted to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it. Now give it to me fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before doing so, you will\NIearn another interesting tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lower half of the cipher I sent to Kogoro, is slightly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lower three numerals were changed to stand for alphabets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Al-Alphabets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. One capital and two small case letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Libra, the Balance. A Latin for the balance scale shortened to I I B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Libra?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know? You wear it on your lapel, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lawyers' pin in the form of the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then. Kogoro Mouri might go to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably went and did it cause he sent me back that mail of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-E-T THEM O-U-T,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take them outside-the house to reduce the number of bad guys
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you have no...\NHands in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you there? Show up guys, you're up there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so slow, come on up guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss. It's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So quick isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who... who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't get it really, but\NI called the police already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I just hope I did something right for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police arrived in time to securely
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,protect Kazuha and Mr. Kusukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dishonest lawyer and her two men were arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the case of the cipher, illegal tax evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And confinement was solved and closed in anzinstant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you used that voice changer to, mimic her voice and lured them to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you used that anesthetic gun and a soccer ball to knock them down, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was great, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can thank me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to come out of the toilet of a restaurant to go up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't leave like you did back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,things wouldn't have gotten as complicated as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'have no idea that'd you'd be held up by a middle-aged lady like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Kid's lunch's gotten cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be with you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Kid's lunch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran sometimes orders it for a nice kid like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it served as a hint for solving the cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the red circle on the flag and the one on the die is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why did Mr. Kusukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why did you go to her to talk her out of doing wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,despite knowing thatyou'd be great bait for the mass media.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time ago. Mr. Kusukawa's mom got help from that lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His mother suffered great losses in-a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,fraud and that-lawyer helped her at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so his mother is very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of this memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to her to talk her out of doingillegal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really in deep water when you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What deep water are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the time when you really wanted to tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to tell me when you felt me trembling against your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better not hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told me you'd tell until I get tired of hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's uh... It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was?
